<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>UI Toolkit Migration — Exploration</title>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/marked/marked.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mermaid@10/dist/mermaid.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/js-yaml@4/dist/js-yaml.min.js"></script>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0f1419;
    --bg-elev: #1a2028;
    --bg-card: #232b35;
    --fg: #e6edf3;
    --fg-dim: #8b949e;
    --accent: #4a9eff;
    --accent-2: #7ee787;
    --danger: #d65151;
    --warn: #f0b429;
    --border: #2d3744;
    --code-bg: #0d1117;
    --space: 12px;
    --radius: 8px;
    --maxw: 1100px;
    --font: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    --mono: "SF Mono", Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: var(--bg); color: var(--fg); font-family: var(--font); line-height: 1.55; }
  a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
  a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  code { font-family: var(--mono); background: var(--code-bg); padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.9em; }
  pre { background: var(--code-bg); padding: 14px; border-radius: var(--radius); overflow-x: auto; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  pre code { background: none; padding: 0; }

  .layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr; min-height: 100vh; }
  aside.toc {
    background: var(--bg-elev);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 24px 16px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    height: 100vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
  }
  aside.toc h2 { font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--fg-dim); margin: 0 0 12px; }
  aside.toc ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  aside.toc li { margin: 2px 0; }
  aside.toc a {
    display: block;
    padding: 5px 8px;
    color: var(--fg);
    font-size: 13px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border-left: 2px solid transparent;
  }
  aside.toc a:hover { background: var(--bg-card); text-decoration: none; }
  aside.toc a.active { border-left-color: var(--accent); background: var(--bg-card); color: var(--accent); }
  aside.toc .lvl-3 { padding-left: 18px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--fg-dim); }

  main { padding: 32px 48px; max-width: var(--maxw); }
  header.doc-head {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-bottom: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  header.doc-head h1 { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 28px; }
  .meta-chips { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 12px; }
  .chip {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
  }
  .chip strong { color: var(--fg); }

  .frontmatter-panel {
    background: var(--bg-elev);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    margin: 16px 0 24px;
  }
  .frontmatter-panel summary {
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    user-select: none;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .frontmatter-panel[open] summary { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .frontmatter-panel .fm-body { padding: 12px 16px; }
  .fm-body pre { margin: 0; font-size: 12px; }

  h1, h2, h3, h4 { color: var(--fg); margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  h2 { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 6px; font-size: 22px; }
  h3 { font-size: 18px; color: var(--accent-2); }
  h4 { font-size: 15px; color: var(--fg-dim); }

  table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 14px 0; font-size: 14px; }
  th, td { padding: 8px 10px; border: 1px solid var(--border); text-align: left; vertical-align: top; }
  th { background: var(--bg-card); color: var(--fg); }
  tr:nth-child(even) td { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015); }

  blockquote { border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); margin: 14px 0; padding: 4px 14px; color: var(--fg-dim); background: var(--bg-elev); border-radius: 0 var(--radius) var(--radius) 0; }

  ul, ol { padding-left: 24px; }
  li { margin: 4px 0; }
  hr { border: 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 28px 0; }

  .stages-section {
    background: var(--bg-elev);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    margin: 16px 0;
  }
  .stage-card {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .stage-card:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .stage-card summary {
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    list-style: none;
    user-select: none;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .stage-card summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .stage-card summary::before {
    content: "▶";
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: transform 0.15s;
    font-size: 10px;
  }
  .stage-card[open] summary::before { transform: rotate(90deg); }
  .stage-id {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--bg);
    padding: 2px 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .stage-title { font-weight: 600; flex: 1; }
  .stage-body { padding: 0 18px 16px; }
  .stage-exit { color: var(--accent-2); font-size: 13px; margin: 8px 0; }
  .stage-exit strong { color: var(--fg); }
  .task-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 12px 0 0; }
  .task-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .task-head { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .task-id { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--accent); background: var(--bg-elev); padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 3px; }
  .task-prefix { font-size: 10px; padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 3px; background: var(--warn); color: var(--bg); font-weight: 700; }
  .task-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; }
  .task-digest { font-size: 13px; color: var(--fg-dim); margin: 4px 0; line-height: 1.5; }
  .task-paths { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--accent-2); margin-top: 6px; }
  .task-paths span { display: inline-block; background: var(--bg-elev); padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 3px; margin: 2px 4px 2px 0; }
  .task-deps { font-size: 11px; color: var(--fg-dim); }
  .task-deps strong { color: var(--warn); }

  .red-proof {
    background: rgba(214,81,81,0.08);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--danger);
    padding: 8px 12px;
    margin: 10px 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius) var(--radius) 0;
  }
  .red-proof strong { color: var(--danger); }

  .controls-bar {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin: 12px 0 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--fg);
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-family: var(--font);
  }
  .btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }

  .search-box {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--fg);
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .search-box:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--accent); }
  .hidden { display: none !important; }

  .mermaid { background: var(--bg-elev); padding: 14px; border-radius: var(--radius); border: 1px solid var(--border); text-align: center; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    aside.toc { position: relative; height: auto; max-height: 280px; }
    main { padding: 20px; }
  }

  /* ===== Enriched visual sections ===== */
  .visual-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin: 16px 0 24px;
  }
  .visual-card {
    background: var(--bg-elev);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .visual-card img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 180px;
    object-fit: contain;
    background: #fff;
    display: block;
  }
  .visual-card.tall img { height: 240px; }
  .visual-card figcaption {
    padding: 10px 14px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .visual-card figcaption strong { color: var(--fg); display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 14px; }
  .visual-card figcaption a { font-size: 11px; }

  /* Stack comparison */
  .stack-compare {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 40px 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
    margin: 16px 0 24px;
    align-items: stretch;
  }
  .stack-col {
    background: var(--bg-elev);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 14px;
  }
  .stack-col h4 { margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--accent); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
  .stack-col.target h4 { color: var(--accent-2); }
  .stack-layer {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .stack-layer .layer-name { font-weight: 600; }
  .stack-layer .layer-meta { font-size: 11px; color: var(--fg-dim); margin-top: 2px; font-family: var(--mono); }
  .stack-arrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 24px;
  }
  .stack-col.legacy .stack-layer { border-left: 3px solid var(--danger); }
  .stack-col.target .stack-layer { border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-2); }

  /* Panel heatmap */
  .heatmap-wrap { background: var(--bg-elev); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0 24px; }
  .heatmap-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(13, 1fr);
    gap: 4px;
    margin: 12px 0;
  }
  .heatmap-cell {
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border-radius: 3px;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    cursor: help;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .heatmap-cell.s1 { background: #4a9eff; color: #001; }
  .heatmap-cell.s2 { background: #7ee787; color: #001; }
  .heatmap-cell.s3 { background: #f0b429; color: #001; }
  .heatmap-cell.s4 { background: #d65151; color: #fff; }
  .heatmap-cell.s5 { background: #c178f0; color: #fff; }
  .heatmap-cell.s6 { background: #888; color: #fff; }
  .heatmap-cell:hover { transform: scale(1.15); z-index: 2; box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--fg); }
  .heatmap-cell .lbl { font-size: 8px; padding: 1px 2px; }
  .heatmap-legend { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 10px; }
  .heatmap-legend .lg-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
  .heatmap-legend .lg-swatch { width: 14px; height: 14px; border-radius: 3px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }

  /* Gantt timeline */
  .gantt {
    background: var(--bg-elev);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 16px;
    margin: 16px 0 24px;
  }
  .gantt-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr 80px; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin: 6px 0; }
  .gantt-label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; }
  .gantt-bar-wrap { position: relative; height: 24px; background: var(--bg-card); border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid var(--border); overflow: hidden; }
  .gantt-bar { position: absolute; top: 0; bottom: 0; border-radius: 3px; display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0 8px; font-size: 11px; color: #001; font-weight: 600; }
  .gantt-bar.b1 { background: #4a9eff; }
  .gantt-bar.b2 { background: #7ee787; }
  .gantt-bar.b3 { background: #f0b429; }
  .gantt-bar.b4 { background: #d65151; color: #fff; }
  .gantt-bar.b5 { background: #c178f0; color: #fff; }
  .gantt-bar.b6 { background: #888; color: #fff; }
  .gantt-meta { font-size: 11px; color: var(--fg-dim); text-align: right; }
  .gantt-axis { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 10px; color: var(--fg-dim); margin-top: 6px; padding: 0 140px 0 140px; }

  /* MVVM flow */
  .mvvm-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 18px;
    margin: 16px 0 24px;
  }
  .mvvm-col {
    background: var(--bg-elev);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 16px;
  }
  .mvvm-col h4 { margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 14px; }
  .mvvm-col.legacy h4 { color: var(--danger); }
  .mvvm-col.target h4 { color: var(--accent-2); }
  .mvvm-node {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    margin: 6px 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
  }
  .mvvm-arrow { text-align: center; color: var(--accent); font-size: 18px; margin: 2px 0; }

  /* Decision matrix */
  .decision-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 16px 0 24px;
  }
  .decision-card {
    background: var(--bg-elev);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 14px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
  }
  .decision-card .q-id {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent);
    background: var(--bg-card);
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .decision-card .q-topic { font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .decision-card .q-pick {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-2);
    color: var(--accent-2);
    padding: 6px 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .decision-card .q-rationale { font-size: 12px; color: var(--fg-dim); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* Reference cards */
  .ref-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 16px 0 24px;
  }
  .ref-card {
    background: var(--bg-elev);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 14px;
    transition: transform 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
  }
  .ref-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); border-color: var(--accent); }
  .ref-card .ref-cat {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .ref-card .ref-cat.unity { background: rgba(74,158,255,0.15); color: var(--accent); }
  .ref-card .ref-cat.binding { background: rgba(126,231,135,0.15); color: var(--accent-2); }
  .ref-card .ref-cat.agentic { background: rgba(240,180,41,0.15); color: var(--warn); }
  .ref-card .ref-cat.tooling { background: rgba(214,81,81,0.15); color: var(--danger); }
  .ref-card .ref-cat.design { background: rgba(193,120,240,0.15); color: #c178f0; }
  .ref-card h5 { margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 14px; }
  .ref-card p { margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: var(--fg-dim); line-height: 1.45; }
  .ref-card a { font-size: 12px; }

  /* Strangler intro */
  .strangler-hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 18px;
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--bg-elev);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 16px;
    margin: 16px 0 24px;
  }
  .strangler-hero img { width: 100%; height: 180px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 6px; }
  .strangler-hero p { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--fg-dim); line-height: 1.55; }
  .strangler-hero p strong { color: var(--fg); }

  /* Section header w/ icon */
  .section-h2 { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .section-h2 .ico {
    width: 28px; height: 28px;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  /* Wide image w/ source caption */
  .wide-fig { margin: 18px 0; background: var(--bg-elev); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; }
  .wide-fig img { width: 100%; display: block; background: #fff; max-height: 480px; object-fit: contain; }
  .wide-fig figcaption { padding: 10px 14px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--fg-dim); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .wide-fig figcaption strong { color: var(--fg); }

  /* Tooltip */
  .cell-tooltip {
    position: fixed;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    color: var(--fg);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    padding: 6px 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 11px;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    display: none;
    font-family: var(--mono);
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="layout">
  <aside class="toc">
    <h2>Navigation</h2>
    <input class="search-box" id="tocSearch" placeholder="Filter sections…" />
    <ul id="tocList"></ul>
  </aside>
  <main>
    <header class="doc-head">
      <h1 id="docTitle">UI Toolkit Migration</h1>
      <div id="metaChips" class="meta-chips"></div>
    </header>

    <details class="frontmatter-panel">
      <summary>Document Metadata (frontmatter)</summary>
      <div class="fm-body">
        <pre id="frontmatterRaw"></pre>
      </div>
    </details>

    <div class="controls-bar">
      <button class="btn" id="expandAll">Expand all stages</button>
      <button class="btn" id="collapseAll">Collapse all stages</button>
      <button class="btn" id="toggleTheme">Toggle theme</button>
    </div>

    <!-- ============== VISUAL CONTEXT ============== -->
    <section id="visualContext">
      <h2 class="section-h2"><span class="ico">▣</span>Visual context — UI Toolkit at a glance</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--fg-dim);font-size:14px;">Modern Unity UI stack: <strong style="color:var(--fg);">UXML</strong> (structure) + <strong style="color:var(--fg);">USS</strong> (styling) + <strong style="color:var(--fg);">C#</strong> (logic + binding). Retained-mode renderer replaces uGUI Canvas as Unity 6+ canonical.</p>
      <div class="visual-grid">
        <figure class="visual-card">
          <img src="assets/ui-toolkit-migration/visual-tree.png" alt="Visual tree hierarchy" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption>
            <strong>VisualElement tree</strong>
            Retained-mode hierarchy. Framework owns the tree in memory + reconciles renders against state diffs.
            <a href="https://docs.unity3d.com/Manual/UIE-VisualTree.html" target="_blank">Unity docs ↗</a>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="visual-card">
          <img src="assets/ui-toolkit-migration/ui-builder.png" alt="UI Builder editor screenshot" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption>
            <strong>UI Builder — visual authoring</strong>
            Live UXML/USS edit + preview. Designer-friendly counterpart to the C# binding path. Drag-drop from Library → Hierarchy.
            <a href="https://docs.unity3d.com/Manual/UIBuilder.html" target="_blank">Builder docs ↗</a>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="visual-card">
          <img src="assets/ui-toolkit-migration/data-binding.gif" alt="Data binding live demo" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption>
            <strong>Native data binding (Unity 6)</strong>
            Path-based, two-way. Source change → UI auto-updates. UI input → source mutates. Replaces hand-rolled <code>UiBindRegistry</code>.
            <a href="https://learn.unity.com/tutorial/ui-toolkit-in-unity-6-crafting-custom-controls-with-data-bindings" target="_blank">Tutorial ↗</a>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="visual-card">
          <img src="assets/ui-toolkit-migration/uitk-controls.png" alt="Standard UI controls" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption>
            <strong>Standard controls</strong>
            Button, Toggle, Slider, Foldout, ListView, ScrollView — all <code>VisualElement</code>-derived. Themeable via USS classes.
            <a href="https://docs.unity3d.com/Manual/UIE-Controls.html" target="_blank">Controls docs ↗</a>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="visual-card">
          <img src="assets/ui-toolkit-migration/layout-engine.png" alt="Flexbox layout engine" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption>
            <strong>Flexbox layout</strong>
            CSS-flexbox model. Solves uGUI <code>RectTransform</code> + anchor hell. Responsive layouts without scripts.
            <a href="https://docs.unity3d.com/Manual/UIE-LayoutEngine.html" target="_blank">Layout docs ↗</a>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
